name: Newlands Beck
description:
Introduction

3 or 4 waterfalls on Newlands Beck, coming out of Dale Head Tarn. One fall is about 15m (?); the other drops are much shorter. The gradient of the stream is not particularly sustained. Escape is possible at all times.
